data.description: If you're looking for the perfect river home, look no further!! This gorgeous 2-story home is nestled on the Sopchoppy River in a quiet neighborhood.  The spacious home offers a large family room downstairs with a cozy fireplace.  The downstairs primary bedroom includes a separate fireplace and is spacious with a newly renovated bathroom.  Upstairs bathroom has been renovated with a walk-in tiled shower and large bedrooms for comfort.  The screened back porch is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the river view. The property also includes a 30x40 workshop with a car lift.  A dock awaits on the water for more rest, fishing and relaxation.
